<p>I have two columns called <code>Quantity</code> and <code>Issued Quantity</code>. I want that when I put value in <code>Quantity</code> column, for instance <code>3</code>, the <code>Issued Quantity</code> will automatically generate <code>3</code>. Also I want it to happen the other way around.</p>  <p>The example is on <code>Purchase Order</code> window, <code>PO Line</code> tab. in <code>Quantity</code> section. When I put <code>4</code> in <code>Quantity</code> field, the <code>PO Quantity</code> field automatically generate <code>4</code>.</p>  <p>I try to imitate the column and field but it doesn't work. </p>